title: Toy Story
description: When a flashy new toy named Buzz Lightyear enters the world of a pull-string cowboy named Woody, it sparks an outrageously funny tiff.

title: Finding Nemo
description: When Nemo, a young clownfish, is unexpectedly carried far from home, his father and Dory embark on a journey to find Nemo.

title: Descpicable me 2
description: Vying to be World's Greatest Villain, Gru and his crew of hilarious minions plot the crime of the century: steal the moon -- but he meets his match when three little girls steal his heart.

title: The Incredibles 2
description: The most loved superhero family returns for a new adventure. Mr. Incredible is left to care for the newborn while the Missus is out saving the world, but the going gets tough for the family with the arrival of a powerful new villain.

title: Moana
description: Sing How Far I'll Go (Reprise) in the Style of Cast of Moana (Disney Original). Disney, English, 2016, Key of Am.

title: Raya the Last Dragon
description: Raya, a fallen princess, must track down the legendary last dragon to stop the evil forces that have returned and threaten her world.

title: Aladin
description: In this live-action retelling of 1992 classic, Aladdin and a power-hungry Grand Vizier vie for a magic lamp that can make their deepest wishes come true.

title: Frozen 2
description: Why was Elsa born with magical powers? Together with Anna, Kristoff, Olaf, and Sven, she sets out on a dangerous but remarkable journey to find the answer.

title: Kung Fu Panda
description: As the Dragon Master, Po has endured his fair share of epic challenges but nothing could prepare him for his greatest one yet-as a Kung Fu teacher to a group of rambunctious kids from Panda Village who have been imbued with a mysterious and powerful chi energy. Together they embark on amazing adventures, battle ferocious villains, and become legends!

title: The Little Mermaid
description: Ariel, a mermaid, is off on an adventure to save her father's beloved kingdom from the sea witch Ursula, with her best friends Flounder and Sebastian
